channel.title: XylemX - Switching - 634 Items - Release!
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/25ap17c.png[/img]
I am releasing this because I am wanting to give something to this community. I know I am new but I am hoping to join this community with a BANG! ;)
Download Links:
About Us:
I was inspired by Runescape Private Server developing since I first discovered them, which was merely 4 years ago. I started with the revision 317, and I enjoyed it. But now it's time for me to move on .I will be moving to higher revision servers. Now I am here and I feel like releasing some of my work.
[img]http://img832.imageshack.us/img832/8135/mediax.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/dxdyz6.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/1z5j8sp.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/3590dhx.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2ry3aed.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2rw55ps.png[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/mcvs0k.png[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/zv3dvl.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/xdeekx.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/2vbvl0j.png[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/28v92xw.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/34r6azd.png[/img]
These pictures are nothing compared to what's ingame.
[img]http://img10.imageshack.us/img10/8117/featuresp.png[/img]
-639 Skill Interface -Perfect Curses -Fixed all dupes -Great Bridding / Switching System -Vote4Cash Command -Webclient Ready -Soulwars Cape -Torva, Pernix and Vitrus -Critical Hits -Perfect PVM -Fixed Slayer -Ring of Life Effects -Skillcape Emotes -602 Animations and 634 Items, 317 NPCS -New Rendering Methods for textures -Fun PK -Chaotic Item Sets -Dungeoneering Teleport GFX including use of Kinship Ring -634 Items / Some 711 Items -Korasi Sword -634 Maps (A couple maps need to be fixed) -Amazing combat -Perfect Stability -Much, Much, Much, Much More!
The server ip is still in the client and is still online. Go into client.java and search for 66.90.68.234 and change that to 127.0.0.1
Note this server is still online. The cache downloads from my website which is also active. I have put a lot of work into this so I hope you guys like it! No antileech. Leave a comment if you are using this, only constructive feedback please.
Credits:
%69 to Gabbe for releasing the base that I used. (69) ;P %31 to Me for fixing all the bugs, adding all the things I added.
